57
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:01,880
Kurozumi Kanjuro
Shogun Orochi's Informant

58
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:02,010
Kurozumi Kanjuro
Shogun Orochi's Informant

59
00:04:02,010 --> 00:04:04,350
Kurozumi Kanjuro
Shogun Orochi's Informant

60
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:09,810
I had to cut down all those men
who mistakenly attacked me as their enemy.

61
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:12,270
I apologize for that.

62
00:04:12,270 --> 00:04:15,440
Well, that's alright!

63
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:17,990
Oh! I see you've got something there...

64
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:23,410
It is Kozuki Momonosuke, per your request.

65
00:04:24,410 --> 00:04:27,410
He is Oden's son.

66
00:04:29,790 --> 00:04:35,130
He cut his ropes and attempted to escape
on the way here, so I had to knock him out.

67
00:04:35,550 --> 00:04:37,800
Do not fret. He is alive.

68
00:04:38,260 --> 00:04:41,340
So this is how you treat
your former Kozuki lord's heir...

69
00:04:43,470 --> 00:04:46,220
How cold and heartless of you!

70
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:50,690
Now that my act is over,
he's just another whelp to me.

71
00:04:51,770 --> 00:04:53,150
What a surprise!

72
00:04:53,150 --> 00:04:55,150
I do remember you.

73
00:04:55,650 --> 00:05:01,660
You're one of the Nine Red Scabbards
that I fought against twenty years ago.

74
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:08,870
And you... I definitely remember you.

75
00:05:09,410 --> 00:05:12,630
Your father was brave, but you're
nothing but a disappointment.

76
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:15,670
You haven't changed one bit in twenty years!

77
00:05:19,260 --> 00:05:21,720
Indeed. He's nothing more
than a miserable brat...

78
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:24,890
who happened to inherit a great name.

79
00:05:25,970 --> 00:05:28,140
You poor thing.

80
00:05:29,390 --> 00:05:32,900
He's bleeding... How could you
strike a little boy so hard?

81
00:05:36,150 --> 00:05:38,900
It's time to drink! Let's make a toast!

82
00:05:38,900 --> 00:05:43,320
You've done well playing
the part of spy for so long!

83
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,870
Bravo!

84
00:05:44,870 --> 00:05:46,740
No, Shogun Orochi!

85
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:49,750
I failed to intercept the Red Scabbards' plan...

86
00:05:49,750 --> 00:05:56,460
because the Straw Hats
and their allies ambushed us!

87
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:58,750
What?! Failed?!

88
00:05:58,750 --> 00:06:05,010
The rebel forces, 5,400 strong, are
advancing toward Onigashima as we speak!

89
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,850
Unacceptable!

90
00:06:10,850 --> 00:06:13,640
You failed to intercept their plan?!

91
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:16,270
I am deeply sorry!

92
00:06:16,270 --> 00:06:22,070
You're the one who told me that
they'd rendezvous at Tokage Port!

93
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:23,990
Why didn't you exterminate them?!

94
00:06:23,990 --> 00:06:27,070
K-Kin'emon outsmarted me!

95
00:06:28,780 --> 00:06:31,410
I have known him for a long time,

96
00:06:31,410 --> 00:06:34,370
but I underestimated his tactical genius!

97
00:06:34,370 --> 00:06:36,830
Stop with the excuses!

98
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:39,380
Answer me, Kanjuro!

99
00:06:39,380 --> 00:06:43,300
Will the samurai fleet make it to Onigashima?!

100
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:46,430
It seems like we're still safe here, Shogun Orochi.

101
00:06:47,090 --> 00:06:48,050
Fukurokuju!

102
00:06:48,890 --> 00:06:52,100
There are no suspicious ships at the port.

103
00:06:52,730 --> 00:06:57,730
However, three of our
warships have yet to return.

104
00:06:58,730 --> 00:07:04,570
In fact, we have confirmation of four pirates
out on the Performance Floor.

105
00:07:07,450 --> 00:07:09,410
Straw Hat Luffy.

106
00:07:12,370 --> 00:07:14,290
Pirate Hunter Zoro.

107
00:07:16,870 --> 00:07:19,090
Eustass "Captain" Kid.

108
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,920
Soldier of Slaughter Killer.

109
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:29,510
It's very likely that the rest of their
crews are also on the island.

110
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:32,060
If you knew that, why didn't
you report it before?!

111
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:35,310
Sir Queen was handling it,

112
00:07:35,310 --> 00:07:39,230
so I thought it'd be better
not to spoil the banquet.

113
00:07:39,770 --> 00:07:45,570
Whether they're here or not, the fact remains
that all of our forces are here on Onigashima.

114
00:07:46,860 --> 00:07:51,580
Whatever happens, this is
the safest place in the country!

115
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,870
You said it!

116
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:57,620
Drink up, Orochi!

117
00:07:57,620 --> 00:08:00,670
Here, let me pour you a cup.

118
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:07,590
No... I don't want reassurances!

119
00:08:08,300 --> 00:08:11,890
I want a report that
the damn samurai have been slain!

120
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:15,560
Luffy made it inside...

121
00:08:15,930 --> 00:08:17,810
Keep yourself alive!

122
00:08:17,810 --> 00:08:22,150
I'll rescue you for sure!

123
00:08:24,730 --> 00:08:25,990
I must escape!

124
00:08:27,150 --> 00:08:28,400
Black Maria!

125
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:30,200
Give him to me!

126
00:08:30,570 --> 00:08:36,080
That's right! We mustn't forget!
He's the leader of the enemy force!

127
00:08:37,870 --> 00:08:40,920
Set the execution stage!

128
00:08:40,920 --> 00:08:47,470
Once the renowned Kozuki family dies out,
any sparks of loyalty left will fade away completely.

129
00:08:47,470 --> 00:08:49,880
And it'll finally be over!

130
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:54,890
Luffy...!

131
00:08:56,020 --> 00:08:57,480
Everyone...!

132
00:08:58,430 --> 00:09:00,060
Father...!

133
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:06,900
Is that you, Cat?! You're late!

134
00:09:06,900 --> 00:09:08,190
You only just arrived?!

135
00:09:08,190 --> 00:09:09,570
Yeah!
Sail: "Cat"

136
00:09:09,570 --> 00:09:11,700
We just climbed up the falls!

137
00:09:14,990 --> 00:09:16,910
Guardians
Nekomamushi's Subordinates

138
00:09:16,910 --> 00:09:19,620
Don't you know what day and time it is?!

139
00:09:20,580 --> 00:09:25,840
It's the night of the Fire Festival, so we're
just in time for the great battle, aren't we?

140
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:29,090
You-gara shouldn't say that until you get here.

141
00:09:29,090 --> 00:09:33,430
We're already on our way to
the northwestern end of Onigashima.

142
00:09:33,430 --> 00:09:36,430
Got it! See you later then!

143
00:09:36,430 --> 00:09:37,560
No, wait!

144
00:09:37,560 --> 00:09:38,560
Wait, hey!

145
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:39,390
Cat!

146
00:09:40,770 --> 00:09:43,730
That impatience of his remains unchanged.

147
00:09:43,730 --> 00:09:46,730
I just hope they make it in time for our raid.

148
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:51,740
I have not seen Kitty since we got separated...

149
00:09:51,740 --> 00:09:55,450
I bet he's as big as Doggy now, too.

150
00:09:55,450 --> 00:09:59,410
That damn cat... He'd better
get here as fast as he can!

151
00:09:59,410 --> 00:10:02,120
We'll reach the rear door soon!

152
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:07,840
Because of the whirlpools, normal ships
can only approach the island from the front.

153
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:12,800
I hope Kin'emon and Denjiro
were able to reach the rear door safely.

154
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:18,510
Yes! I want all of us to fulfill
Lord Oden's wish together!

155
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:20,600
Lord Momonosuke...

156
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,690
Please be safe!

157
00:10:32,110 --> 00:10:33,740
Are they all okay?

158
00:10:34,700 --> 00:10:36,660
Yeah, of course they are!

159
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:42,200
He said everyone made it to the island
already, so I guess the raid is underway!

160
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:46,830
That lonely island is now
called Onigashima, huh?

161
00:10:46,830 --> 00:10:51,420
Who would've thought that we'd arrive at the
same time, even though you left before me?

162
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:55,380
Turns out I didn't need to entrust you
with my message to Straw Hat Luffy!

163
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:59,050
You're right!

164
00:10:59,050 --> 00:11:00,720
I'll throw this note out!

165
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:06,730
Note: "I'll be late but I'll be there. -Marco"

166
00:11:06,730 --> 00:11:10,230
Anyway, I can't believe you came, Marco.

167
00:11:10,610 --> 00:11:13,190
Well, I always did like Oden.

168
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:21,490
But I can't believe how much
his country has changed...

169
00:11:22,950 --> 00:11:25,580
News about this place never crosses the sea.

170
00:11:25,580 --> 00:11:29,790
I didn't know the once prosperous Wano
had been reduced to such a state...

171
00:11:30,500 --> 00:11:32,960
It's all because of Kaido.

172
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:36,630
If you've made up your mind,
let's hurry on to Onigashima!

173
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:39,260
We must catch up to everyone!

174
00:11:39,260 --> 00:11:40,930
But what can we do?

175
00:11:40,930 --> 00:11:42,930
The raid has already begun.

176
00:11:42,930 --> 00:11:45,390
How will we slip past
the enemy lines to join them?

177
00:11:45,810 --> 00:11:47,440
Leave it to me!

178
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:49,650
I have an idea!

179
00:11:53,610 --> 00:11:59,410
As planned, Denjiro is leading
the southern forces to the castle's rear door.

180
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:59,410
Southern Forces

Denjiro's Group

181
00:12:00,370 --> 00:12:02,370
There seems to be a gate here!

182
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:05,450
Hide!

183
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,380
Is he a top officer?

184
00:12:09,380 --> 00:12:10,460
What rotten luck!

185
00:12:10,460 --> 00:12:13,340
Listen! Find him as quickly as possible!

186
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:13,710
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

187
00:12:14,050 --> 00:12:16,260
On the contrary, it seems we have lucked out.

188
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:18,180
I know him.

189
00:12:18,760 --> 00:12:20,010
I will talk to him.

190
00:12:20,930 --> 00:12:21,800
Who goes there?!

191
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:23,810
Wait, it's me!

192
00:12:23,810 --> 00:12:25,020
Aren't you...?

193
00:12:25,020 --> 00:12:26,480
It's been a while...

194
00:12:26,890 --> 00:12:30,690
Sasaki
Soaring Six
Beast Pirates

195
00:12:27,100 --> 00:12:28,350
Sasaki!

196
00:12:28,350 --> 00:12:29,730
Kyoshiro!

197
00:12:29,730 --> 00:12:31,940
I heard you weren't coming this year!

198
00:12:31,940 --> 00:12:34,070
Yeah, I ask that you keep this a secret.

199
00:12:34,070 --> 00:12:38,030
You're here incognito? What happened to
that pompadour you were so proud of?

200
00:12:38,030 --> 00:12:40,740
It's unusual to see you
away from the banquet.

201
00:12:40,740 --> 00:12:45,040
Yeah. Kaido's kid went missing.

202
00:12:45,450 --> 00:12:47,620
But hey, want a drink?

203
00:12:47,620 --> 00:12:48,710
You bet I do!

204
00:12:48,710 --> 00:12:51,790
Guys! Head back to the Skull Dome!

205
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:53,920
I'll join you later.

206
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:59,970
A gate that was missing from the blueprints.
And one of the Soaring Six, Sasaki.

207
00:12:59,970 --> 00:13:05,260
Such obstacles would have been
difficult for Kyoshiro to overcome

208
00:13:05,260 --> 00:13:08,060
if he wasn't so trusted by the enemy.

209
00:13:09,230 --> 00:13:10,690
Seastone?!

210
00:13:10,690 --> 00:13:12,650
Hey, what's the big idea, Kyoshiro?!

211
00:13:13,230 --> 00:13:14,480
Restrain him!

212
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,520
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

213
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:19,070
What's going on?! Hey!

214
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:21,030
Gag him as well!

215
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:21,860
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

216
00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:23,870
Answer me, Kyoshiro!

217
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:26,080
Hey, Sasaki...

218
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:30,160
How much do you know of Wano's history?

219
00:13:31,290 --> 00:13:32,710
Is that...?!

220
00:13:38,170 --> 00:13:41,130
After restraining one of
the formidable Soaring Six,

221
00:13:41,130 --> 00:13:45,850
Denjiro split his group into two,
just as the eastern forces had.

222
00:13:45,850 --> 00:13:47,720
Get to the dome from here!

223
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:49,270
Good luck!

224
00:13:49,890 --> 00:13:53,600
Dome

Infiltration

Team

225
00:13:50,770 --> 00:13:55,940
Thus, the southern forces
are steadily closing in on Kaido!

226
00:13:54,940 --> 00:13:56,440
Raid Team

227
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:56,520
Raid Team

228
00:13:56,520 --> 00:13:56,610
Raid Team

229
00:13:56,610 --> 00:13:56,690
Raid Team

230
00:13:56,690 --> 00:13:56,770
Raid Team

231
00:13:56,770 --> 00:13:56,860
Raid Team

232
00:13:56,860 --> 00:13:56,940
Raid Team

233
00:13:59,110 --> 00:14:01,450
Eastern

Forces



Kin'emon's

Group

234
00:14:06,530 --> 00:14:07,870
Fire!

235
00:14:14,330 --> 00:14:17,000
I won't let you get away!

236
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,750
I knew it wouldn't work!

237
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:20,210
Of course it didn't!

238
00:14:26,350 --> 00:14:27,720
They're gone!

239
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:29,140
Chobro!

240
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:30,810
That's one fierce mature woman...

241
00:14:34,650 --> 00:14:38,770
Even though they were frightened,
they still led her in the opposite direction...

242
00:14:38,770 --> 00:14:42,530
We are in your debt,
Commander Chopper, Driver Usopp...

243
00:14:43,070 --> 00:14:44,660
Let us carry on!

244
00:14:44,660 --> 00:14:45,950
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

245
00:14:45,950 --> 00:14:49,790
Everyone! Do not let their sacrifice go to waste!

246
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:51,830
Hey, shouldn't we do something?!

247
00:14:51,830 --> 00:14:57,130
I think that monstrous mature woman
is too much for those two boys to handle!

248
00:14:57,130 --> 00:14:58,250
She's right!

249
00:14:58,250 --> 00:14:59,380
It's Big Mom!

250
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:00,550
I know!

251
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:03,050
That's why there's nothing we can do!

252
00:15:03,050 --> 00:15:06,300
Let's just be happy they lured her away!

253
00:15:06,300 --> 00:15:09,510
In any case, why's it so hot in here?

254
00:15:09,510 --> 00:15:11,060
Nami! Look up!

255
00:15:11,060 --> 00:15:12,680
We're in trouble!

256
00:15:14,310 --> 00:15:16,480
I found you!

257
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:21,110
It's the woman who kidnapped Zeus, Mama!

258
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:26,740
Fight, Pay-Pay! Fight, Pay-Pay!

259
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:29,910
Hey! Go look somewhere else, you bonehead!

260
00:15:29,910 --> 00:15:31,410
Excuse me, Pay-Pay?!

261
00:15:31,410 --> 00:15:34,370
How dare you...!

262
00:15:34,370 --> 00:15:35,000
But...

263
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:38,210
I can't run anymore...

264
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:42,210
Pay-Pay! I'm ever so weary!

265
00:15:42,210 --> 00:15:45,920
Woe is me!

266
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:47,510
Don't cry about it to me!

267
00:15:47,510 --> 00:15:49,640
If you're tired, just sit there!

268
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:51,970
You're supposed to offer...

269
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:54,680
Oh, no!

270
00:15:55,890 --> 00:15:59,270
...to carry me on your back!

271
00:15:58,940 --> 00:16:01,940
Ulti and Page One
Soaring Six
Beast Pirates

272
00:15:59,270 --> 00:16:01,940
Hey, get off of me! Hey!

273
00:16:01,940 --> 00:16:04,860
Wait! Let go of me! Big Sis!

274
00:16:05,780 --> 00:16:06,990
You little...

275
00:16:06,990 --> 00:16:08,990
Hey! Stop it! I mean it!

276
00:16:11,580 --> 00:16:13,330
Pay-Pay?!

277
00:16:13,330 --> 00:16:15,950
Pay-Pay! Pay-Pay! Pay-Pay!

278
00:16:16,330 --> 00:16:19,250
Stay with me, stay with me, stay with me!

279
00:16:19,250 --> 00:16:24,670
Oh no, my Pay-Pay!

280
00:16:29,130 --> 00:16:29,840
What's that?

281
00:16:30,930 --> 00:16:32,470
Pay-Pay!

282
00:16:32,470 --> 00:16:37,100
Pay-Pay sacrificed himself to save me!

283
00:16:40,730 --> 00:16:42,520
Who the hell are you?!

284
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:44,320
Who the hell are you?!

285
00:16:56,370 --> 00:17:00,330
There it is... Onigashima.

286
00:17:01,330 --> 00:17:02,790
King...

287
00:17:03,670 --> 00:17:05,090
Marco...

288
00:17:06,420 --> 00:17:08,050
Straw Hat...

289
00:17:08,970 --> 00:17:11,890
They'd better prepare
themselves for a licking...

290
00:17:11,890 --> 00:17:14,180
And no, I don't approve of Mama's alliance!

291
00:17:14,180 --> 00:17:18,890
The Big Mom Pirates will have the last lick!

292
00:17:20,690 --> 00:17:21,980
What now, Usopp?!

293
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:26,940
Big Mom turned back
to go after Nami and the others!

294
00:17:27,440 --> 00:17:30,110
I guess she's trying to take back Zeus.

295
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:32,110
I'm worried about them...

296
00:17:32,110 --> 00:17:36,790
The transformation switch seems
to have activated when she punched us.

297
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:40,290
Well, I'm sure they'll be fine...
Sanji's with them, too.

298
00:17:40,710 --> 00:17:41,960
Sanji, huh?

299
00:17:42,370 --> 00:17:47,750
I hope he remembers to rescue Momonosuke
instead of chasing women in the pleasure hall.

300
00:17:47,750 --> 00:17:50,760
I wouldn't rule that out...

301
00:17:50,760 --> 00:17:52,880
But let's trust Sanji!

302
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:54,300
Yeah!

303
00:17:55,760 --> 00:18:00,350
Kin'emon's team was able
to advance, so we're doing well!

304
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:04,610
We showed them what
the Brachio-Tank is capable of!

305
00:18:04,610 --> 00:18:10,490
Yeah! We're Commander Chopper and
gunner Usopp driving the Brachio-Tank 5!

306
00:18:10,490 --> 00:18:14,200
Nothing stands in our way!

307
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:18,540
Inside

the

Pleasure

Hall

308
00:18:23,670 --> 00:18:25,920
Come along...

309
00:18:30,130 --> 00:18:32,630
An old umbrella.

310
00:18:34,090 --> 00:18:37,680
Old clogs and old sandals.

311
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:43,850
A dirt wall!

312
00:18:43,850 --> 00:18:46,520
A candle!

313
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:53,070
A lantern, too!

314
00:18:57,280 --> 00:19:00,870
I give you life!

315
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:05,170
So follow me.

316
00:19:06,710 --> 00:19:08,920
Mama, this way!

317
00:19:09,340 --> 00:19:12,920
Hey! Stop calling for Big Mom, sun!

318
00:19:14,760 --> 00:19:16,430
What should I do, Nami?!

319
00:19:16,430 --> 00:19:20,140
If she catches me, I'm a goner!

320
00:19:21,520 --> 00:19:24,980
Is that overripe mature woman
really that dangerous?

321
00:19:24,980 --> 00:19:27,650
She's on a whole different level!

322
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:31,480
Hey, didn't we see Sanji a little while ago?

323
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:33,650
Yeah!

324
00:19:33,650 --> 00:19:35,450
Oh, but...

325
00:19:36,110 --> 00:19:38,120
Sorry for making you worry...

326
00:19:38,910 --> 00:19:41,450
I'm not giving up on finding those women!

327
00:19:43,250 --> 00:19:45,210
What did he even come here for?!

328
00:19:46,330 --> 00:19:50,250
In any case, we need to outrun her
and look for Lord Momonosuke!

329
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:53,880
Okay!

330
00:19:57,260 --> 00:20:00,680
Mama! This way!

331
00:20:04,060 --> 00:20:05,680
There's no need to rush.

332
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:08,690
The Performance Floor is just ahead.

333
00:20:08,690 --> 00:20:10,980
There's nowhere to run.

334
00:20:20,370 --> 00:20:22,910
So many of these guys have powers…

335
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:27,080
Call us Gifters.

336
00:20:30,380 --> 00:20:35,010
We, too, once aimed to be King of the Pirates.

337
00:20:35,840 --> 00:20:39,050
If you bow down to Lord Kaido,
things will be easier for you.

338
00:20:39,550 --> 00:20:41,600
There are almost 500 of us.

339
00:20:42,180 --> 00:20:44,010
Don't make this hard on yourself.

340
00:20:44,010 --> 00:20:45,850
It's not too late to start over.

341
00:20:48,560 --> 00:20:52,440
Kid! I told you it's too reckless
to break through head-on!

342
00:20:53,270 --> 00:20:56,940
We got separated from Heat and the others...

343
00:20:56,940 --> 00:20:59,360
They were fighting right alongside us,

344
00:20:57,030 --> 00:20:59,700
Wire
Kid Pirates
Heat
Kid Pirates

345
00:20:59,360 --> 00:21:01,620
but they'll be okay on their own.

346
00:21:01,620 --> 00:21:07,000
If we kill you guys, I bet we'll get promoted!

347
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:12,000
Please stop!

348
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:13,710
Lord Kaido is looking for you!

349
00:21:13,710 --> 00:21:15,340
Stop bothering me!

350
00:21:15,340 --> 00:21:17,170
Leave me alone!

351
00:21:17,170 --> 00:21:20,130
– Young Master! Please stop!
– Young Master! Please stop!

352
00:21:20,130 --> 00:21:24,180
Let down your guard and you die!

353
00:21:29,850 --> 00:21:32,850
Pay-Pay!

354
00:21:32,850 --> 00:21:36,820
Pay-Pay! Are you okay?!

355
00:21:37,150 --> 00:21:42,740
Don't leave me! I'd be ever so distraught!

356
00:21:42,740 --> 00:21:44,120
Hey, you!

357
00:21:45,620 --> 00:21:46,830
How could you...

358
00:21:46,830 --> 00:21:49,870
How could you do this to Pay-Pay?!

359
00:21:49,870 --> 00:21:54,630
Don't you dare bully my Pay-Pay!

360
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:02,010
You're the one who used him
to ski down the stairs.

361
00:22:03,760 --> 00:22:05,100
What's your name?!

362
00:22:05,100 --> 00:22:08,140
Who do you work for
and which unit do you belong to?!

363
00:22:08,140 --> 00:22:10,730
No, Big Sis...

364
00:22:11,520 --> 00:22:13,310
He's an intruder.

365
00:22:13,310 --> 00:22:15,110
What?!

366
00:22:15,560 --> 00:22:17,110
I'm Luffy.

367
00:22:17,650 --> 00:22:20,280
The man who'll become the King of the Pirates!

368
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:35,670
Do you have any idea
whose castle you're standing in?

369
00:22:36,170 --> 00:22:41,170
The one who will become
King of the Pirates is obviously Lord Kaido!

370
00:22:44,260 --> 00:22:47,350
You freaking dumbass!

371
00:22:48,050 --> 00:22:52,230
I'll cave your damn skull in!

372
00:22:52,850 --> 00:22:54,020
A headbutt?!

373
00:22:54,850 --> 00:22:57,480
Ulti-Mortar!

374
00:23:28,600 --> 00:23:30,810
Hey, Big Sis!

375
00:23:31,430 --> 00:23:33,020
I know...

376
00:23:39,150 --> 00:23:41,360
Pay-Pay too?

377
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:42,190
Yeah!

378
00:24:11,470 --> 00:24:14,640
Excuse me, but...

379
00:24:15,100 --> 00:24:18,100
why did you two transform?!

380
00:24:19,060 --> 00:24:22,900
Ulti
